    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Diabetes mellitus.

          2. Cardiac disease.

          3. Essential hypertension.

          4. Chronic chest disease, and/or chronic TB infection.

          5. Chronic hepatitis.

          6. Neurologic disease.

          7. Anaemia (Hemoglobin &lt;10 gm/dL).

          8. Thyroid disease.

          9. Multiple pregnancy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant women &lt; 34 weeks.
      </textblock>
